Learning Management System

 Interactive and Animated Learning Management System (LMS) offers a modern, 
 engaging platform for online education. Designed to enhance both teaching and learning experiences, 
 this LMS features a visually appealing interface enriched with smooth animations and interactive elements. 
 Instructors can effortlessly create multimedia-rich courses using a drag-and-drop builder, incorporating videos, quizzes, puzzles, and real-time collaboration tools. 

✨ Key Features
🌐 Modern UI/UX with Framer Motion / GSAP animations

📚 Drag-and-drop course builder for instructors

📊 Gamification: XP, badges, leaderboards, progress bars

🧠 Interactive lessons with quizzes, videos, puzzles, and animations

💬 Live chat, discussion forums, and instructor messaging

📜 Auto-certification with animated certificate intro

📈 Admin analytics dashboard with animated charts

🧑‍💻 Roles & User Types
👨‍🎓 Students: Take interactive courses, track progress, earn rewards

👩‍🏫 Instructors: Build multimedia courses, grade assessments

👨‍💼 Admins: Manage platform data, users, and performance analytics
